	<region id="editorData">
		<node id="editorData">
			<attribute id="HowToTrigger" type="LSString" value="* Have at least 2 characters in your party.&#xD;&#xA;* goto -542; 27; 464, approach Philomeen with the 1 character&#xD;&#xA;* While that character is in the dialog, approach the runepowder barrel (next to her) with another character.&#xD;&#xA;* She will drop her dialog and will play this AD, then explode." />
			<attribute id="needLayout" type="bool" value="False" />
			<attribute id="nextNodeId" type="uint32" value="1" />
			<attribute id="synopsis" type="LSString" value="* The idea: &quot;I told you not another step forward, but another of yours sneaks in!&quot;&#xD;&#xA;* Philomeen is playing this AD right before exploding the runepowder barrel, if another player approaches it while she is in her normal dialog (UND_PanicRoom_HiddenGnome).&#xD;&#xA;* This AD is supposed to be short but clear." />
